text: Athoumane Solihi (born 30 March 1991) is a Comorian swimmer. He competed in the men's 50 metre freestyle event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where he ranked 76th with a time of 27.31 seconds. He did not advance to the semifinals. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Comorian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Comoros Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Male freestyle swimmers
